{"tid":1579634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚同今晚美國人都話左比我地知有幾樣野要繼續","createTime":"2019-09-18T16:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T16:44:01.000Z","uid":142716,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"abeae6d53a2cd04fe6a49d7c0d04186a296daa1c","tid":1579634,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:07:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 美國國旗</span><br />\n<br />\n人地讚我地舉旗啊 識做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BjiLR01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBjiLR01.jpg&h=72db2309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 美國國歌</span><br />\n<br />\n仲有個令星期，就算係英文都聽熟背熟佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxoCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=7ddc7efa\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. Twitter </span><br />\n人地開到聲唔係唔多謝返人啊嘛? <br />\n不過記住<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好淨係提Trump啊</span></span><br />\n我地做既大小事佢地真係知嫁<br />\n連十點大嗌，人鏈佢地都知<br />\n所以國際文宣極重要！！！<br />\n繼續文宣唔好比佢停啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國咁高調出左聲對家都實會大大力抹黑<br />\n所以我地一定要洗返地<br />\n邊個仲未開twitter！快啲去開！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#HongKongHumanRightsandDemocracyAct<br />\n#StandwithHongKong<br />\n#LiberateHongkong<br />\n#Hongkongprotest<br />\n#5demandsnot1less<br />\n#HongKongPolice<br />\n#PoliceTerrorism<br />\n#PoliceBrutalitiy<br />\n#SOSHK<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"283e85de9f511a16d37fe36d0a9301ffaa01bc53","tid":1579634,"uid":142716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:08:18.000Z","msg":"Sir, this way<img src=\"/assets/face